Don't you mean Shurima / Risen / Forced thematic / Gardien of the sand Zac? {{item:3069}} 

Joke aside, Zac would make a great sandman, even if I think it would need a lot of particles and different sound effect (sand doesn't go "Blob!")
Frankly, I love Zac, and he didn't have a skin in such a long time, I'd buy any new skin for him.
